OL,3,CFirst-time buyer 'excited' to discover
OL,4,Cher home is an old abbey
OL,6,FMoving into your first home can be a
OL,7,Fbusy time, especially if the place
OL,8,Fneeds a bit of sprucing up.
OL,10,FBut Kirsten Markham got a bit more
OL,11,Fthan she bargained for from her house
OL,12,Fin Kidwelly, Carmarthenshire, when she
OL,13,Fdiscovered it was actually a former
OL,14,Fabbey.
OL,16,FThe 23-year-old realised something was
OL,17,Fup when she started renovations at the
OL,18,Fempty property in the town,
OL,19,Fappropriately located on Abbey Street.
