OL,3,CFirst-time buyer 'excited' to discover
OL,4,Cher home is an old abbey
OL,6,F"I started uncovering amazing
OL,7,Ffeatures, and so much history," she
OL,8,Fsaid.J"So that's when the journey
OL,9,Fbegan. It was amazing to discover a
OL,10,Fhouse with a story."
OL,12,FThings took an unexpected turn when a
OL,13,Fneighbour suggested the terraced house
OL,14,Fmight once have served a religious
OL,15,Fpurpose.
OL,17,F"The neighbour came over and started
OL,18,Ftalking about the cellar," she
OL,19,Fexplained.
