OL,3,CFirst-time buyer 'excited' to discover
OL,4,Cher home is an old abbey
OL,6,F"The first thing people would say was
OL,7,Fit was an abbey, but I couldn't find a
OL,8,Flot of history on the house and the
OL,9,Fstreet itself. So it's very hard to to
OL,10,Fsort of determine what it actually was.
OL,12,F"But now the house is fully stripped,
OL,13,Fyou can see all of the lovely old
OL,14,Ffeatures and the history."
OL,16,FKeith Evans, of the Kidwelly History
OL,17,FSociety, says the building may date
OL,18,Fback to the 12th century.
