OL,3,CFirst-time buyer 'excited' to discover
OL,4,Cher home is an old abbey
OL,6,F"We think this site would have been
OL,7,Fagricultural to start off with, used
OL,8,Fby the church for growing crops,
OL,9,Fsheep, having cattle and dairy," he
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"And then over the centuries, from
OL,13,Faround about 1110 to when it closed in
OL,14,F1544 under Henry VIII, buildings like
OL,15,Fthis would have gone up with different
OL,16,Fuses, perhaps for storage."
OL,18,FLocal historians think Kirsten's
OL,19,Fexperience could be the tip of the
OL,20,Ficeberg, with much more undiscovered
OL,21,Fhistory in Carmarthenshire and beyond.
