OL,3,CFirst-time buyer 'excited' to discover
OL,4,Cher home is an old abbey
OL,6,F"There's a lot of archaeological work
OL,7,Fthat hasn't been done in Kidwelly, and
OL,8,Fyet Kidwelly is one of the principal
OL,9,Fmediaeval settlements for Wales,"
OL,10,Fadded Mr Evans.
OL,12,F"We would hope that Kirsten's
OL,13,Fexperience would encourage other local
OL,14,Fpeople to have a look at the
OL,15,Fstructures that lie behind years of
OL,16,Fdifferent alterations (to their homes).
OL,18,F"We just hope that events like this
OL,19,Fwill encourage people across the whole
OL,20,Fof Wales to start looking into the
OL,21,Fhistory of their own communities."
