OL,3,CFirst-time buyer 'excited' to discover
OL,4,Cher home is an old abbey
OL,6,FFor now, though, Kirsten is just
OL,7,Flooking forward to uncovering more of
OL,8,Fthe unique secrets of her new home.
OL,10,F"I'd say don't be scared - just jump
OL,11,Fin," she added.
OL,13,F"I would definitely encourage buying a
OL,14,Fhouse like this that has history and
OL,15,Fjust stripping it and working with
OL,16,Fwhat you have.
OL,18,F"Now I can begin to start discovering
OL,19,Fmore history about the house, and I'm
OL,20,Freally excited about that."
